@echo off
COLOR 09
title Your Server

echo -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
echo /                                                                             \
echo /                               Now compiling server...                       \
echo /                                                                             \
echo -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\javac" -cp . *.java

echo -------------------------------------------------------------------------------
echo /                                                                             \
echo /                              Now starting server...                         \
echo /                                                                             \
echo -------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_02\bin\java" server
pause
